comment: * A class that exposes the methods to register and obtain each system service.

methods.name: public IBinder get()
methods.comment:
* Get the system server binding object for a service. * *

This blocks until the service instance is ready, * or a timeout happens, in which case it returns null.

methods.comment:
* Get the system server binding object for a service. * *

This blocks until the service instance is ready, * or a timeout happens, in which case it throws {@link ServiceNotFoundException}.

methods.name: public IBinder tryGet()
methods.comment:
* Get the system server binding object for a service. If the specified service is
         * not available, it returns null.
